=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 05, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104smq1665702815171.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/smq1665702815171.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/smq1665702815171.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"smq1665702815171\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Character Set Section\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Each translation table can include up to 128 character sets (numbered 0 through 127).\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"smq1665702815171__topic_d63710e1_d63711e1_d63712e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"smq1665702815171__p_d63713e1_d63714e1_d63715e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">^begin_set</code> {<var class=\"keyword varname\">CharacterSetNumber</var>}</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"smq1665702815171__p_d63716e1_d63717e1_d63718e1\">{<code class=\"ph codeph\">^CHR</code>{<code class=\"ph codeph\">/8</code>} <code class=\"ph codeph\">FONT_</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Number</var> {<var class=\"keyword varname\">Description</var>} }</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"smq1665702815171__p_d63719e1_d63720e1_d63721e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">OutputCharacterCode</var> {<var class=\"keyword varname\">Number</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">.</code>}<var class=\"keyword varname\">MetaCharacter</var> | <var class=\"keyword varname\">UnifaceMnemonic</var> {<var class=\"keyword varname\">Description</var>}</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"smq1665702815171__p_d63722e1_d63723e1_d63724e1\">...</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"smq1665702815171__p_d63725e1_d63726e1_d63727e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">^end_set</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"smq1665702815171__section_hbd_rth_hcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d97885e112\">Delimitors</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"smq1665702815171__table_d5555e1_d5556e1_d5557e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"smq1665702815171__table_d5555e1_d5556e1_d5557e1__entry__1\">Mnemonic </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"smq1665702815171__table_d5555e1_d5556e1_d5557e1__entry__2\">Explanation </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"smq1665702815171__table_d5555e1_d5556e1_d5557e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">begin_set</code>\n</p>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">CharacterSetNumber</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"smq1665702815171__table_d5555e1_d5556e1_d5557e1__entry__2\">Mark start of character set definition.\n                     </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"smq1665702815171__table_d5555e1_d5556e1_d5557e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">end_set</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"smq1665702815171__table_d5555e1_d5556e1_d5557e1__entry__2\">Mark end of character set definition. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"smq1665702815171__section_x2l_sth_hcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d97885e174\">Arguments</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"smq1665702815171__ul_agy_sth_hcc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"smq1665702815171__li_d27782e1_d27783e1_d27784e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">CharacterSetNumber</var>—Number\n               identifying the character set; optional. If omitted, the next sequential number\n               (0-127) is assigned. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"smq1665702815171__li_d27785e1_d27786e1_d27787e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Number</var>—Uniface font number,\n               which identifies a meta character set; value values are 0 through 7. For more\n               information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tkv1665702983600.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tkv1665702983600.html\" title=\"In principle, each Uniface font can contain characters from any of the defined character sets. In practice, however, an entire character set is often mapped to a single font. To aid this mapping, Uniface provides functions which map an entire character set in one step, without explicitly defining each character.\">Character Set Mappings</a>. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"smq1665702815171__li_d27788e1_d27789e1_d27790e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">OutputCharacterCode</var>—Device\n               characters to which Uniface chcarcters or functions are mapped. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"smq1665702815171__li_d27791e1_d27792e1_d27793e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">MetaCharacter</var>—Character in the\n               specified Uniface meta character set. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"smq1665702815171__li_d27794e1_d27795e1_d27796e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">UnifaceMnemonic</var>—Uniface\n               mnemonic code recognized by the device translation table compiler. For allowed\n               mnemonics, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hdh1665702981923.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hdh1665702981923.html\" title=\"Uniface uses a set of mnemonics to identify particular functions. When you define a device translation table, you define the device control codes that implement a particular function.\">Device Translation Table Mnemonics</a>. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"smq1665702815171__li_d27797e1_d27798e1_d27799e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Description</var>—optional\n               description or comments. </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"smq1665702815171__p_d63734e1_d63735e1_d63736e1\">The following example shows some definitions from the\n            standard USYSTERM table:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"smq1665702815171__pre_jwl_5th_hcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">^^ USYSTERM (VT220) device display and printer definitions table\nBEGIN_SET begin normal ASCII set\n^esc(B select ascii set selection\n^chr font_0 map (32-126) to 0.(32-196)\nEND_SET\nBEGIN_SET begin Multinational set\n^esc(&lt; select multination set selection\n^chr font_1 map (32-126) to 1.(32-196)\n) view_cc map copyright character\nEND_SET\nBEGIN_SET begin special graphic set\n^esc(0 select special graphic set selection\n^chr font_7 (32-126) to 7.(32-196)\na view_frame map FRAME character\n` view_menu map MENU character\nb view_ht map HT (horizontal tab)\nc view_ff map FF (formfeed)\nd view_cr map CR (carret)\nl top_left map top Left corner\nw top_con map top connector\nk top_right map top Right corner\nq top_line map top line\nt mid_left map left middle corner\nn mid_con map middle connector\nu mid_right map right middle corner\nq mid_line map middle line\nm bot_left map bottom Left corner\nv bot_con map bottom middle connector\nj bot_right map bottom right corner\nq bot_line map bottom line\nx vert_left map left vertical line\nx vert_mid map middle vertical line\nx vert_right map right vertical line\no view_top map view entity top line\no view_mid map view entity middle line\ns view_bot map view entity bottom line\n~ view_vert map view entity left/right vertical\nEND_SET\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532057\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532057\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Character Set Section Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 05, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Character Set Section Each translation table can include up to 128 character sets (numbered 0 through 127). ^begin_set { CharacterSetNumber } { ^CHR { /8 } FONT_ Number { Description } } OutputCharacterCode { Number . } MetaCharacter | UnifaceMnemonic { Description } ... ^end_set Delimitors Mnemonic Explanation begin_set CharacterSetNumber Mark start of character set definition. end_set Mark end of character set definition. Arguments CharacterSetNumber —Number identifying the character set; optional. If omitted, the next sequential number (0-127) is assigned. Number —Uniface font number, which identifies a meta character set; value values are 0 through 7. For more information, see Character Set Mappings . OutputCharacterCode —Device characters to which Uniface chcarcters or functions are mapped. MetaCharacter —Character in the specified Uniface meta character set. UnifaceMnemonic —Uniface mnemonic code recognized by the device translation table compiler. For allowed mnemonics, see Device Translation Table Mnemonics . Description —optional description or comments. The following example shows some definitions from the standard USYSTERM table: ^^ USYSTERM (VT220) device display and printer definitions table BEGIN_SET begin normal ASCII set ^esc(B select ascii set selection ^chr font_0 map (32-126) to 0.(32-196) END_SET BEGIN_SET begin Multinational set ^esc(< select multination set selection ^chr font_1 map (32-126) to 1.(32-196) ) view_cc map copyright character END_SET BEGIN_SET begin special graphic set ^esc(0 select special graphic set selection ^chr font_7 (32-126) to 7.(32-196) a view_frame map FRAME character ` view_menu map MENU character b view_ht map HT (horizontal tab) c view_ff map FF (formfeed) d view_cr map CR (carret) l top_left map top Left corner w top_con map top connector k top_right map top Right corner q top_line map top line t mid_left map left middle corner n mid_con map middle connector u mid_right map right middle corner q mid_line map middle line m bot_left map bottom Left corner v bot_con map bottom middle connector j bot_right map bottom right corner q bot_line map bottom line x vert_left map left vertical line x vert_mid map middle vertical line x vert_right map right vertical line o view_top map view entity top line o view_mid map view entity middle line s view_bot map view entity bottom line ~ view_vert map view entity left/right vertical END_SET Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}